OL,3,CMet Police chief hits out at 'army of
OL,4,Carmchair commentators' who film
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FThe head of Britain's biggest police
OL,8,Fforce has hit out at "armchair
OL,9,Fcommentators" who film officers while
OL,10,Fon duty.
OL,12,FMet Police Commissioner Sir Mark
OL,13,FRowley claimed the prospect of
OL,14,Ffrequently being filmed and later
OL,15,Fcritiqued on social media might put
OL,16,Foff future recruits from joining the
OL,17,Fpolice.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@MO]
