OL,3,CMet Police chief hits out at 'army of
OL,4,Carmchair commentators' who film
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FIn the piece, first posted on business
OL,8,Fnetworking site LinkedIn, he said:
OL,9,F"The reality is that policing is
OL,10,Fcomplex, challenging and can look
OL,11,Fmessy.
OL,13,F"We expect officers to arrive on scene
OL,14,Fquickly and act with limited
OL,15,Finformation based on what they see.
OL,17,F"They don't have the benefit of being
OL,18,Fable to watch a full incident unfold
OL,19,Fbefore deciding what to do, they have
OL,20,Fto be decisive and act quickly.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
