OL,3,CMet Police chief hits out at 'army of
OL,4,Carmchair commentators' who film
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,F"And they do so in the glare of
OL,8,Fhundreds of people ready to film their
OL,9,Fevery moment.
OL,11,F"There aren't many professions where
OL,12,Ffrom the minute you arrive at an
OL,13,Fincident to the minute you leave, you
OL,14,Fare filmed and then critiqued by an
OL,15,Farmy of armchair commentators.
OL,17,F"Yet this is what happens to our
OL,18,Fofficers and they still come back to
OL,19,Fwork the next day.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
