OL,3,CMet Police chief hits out at 'army of
OL,4,Carmchair commentators' who film
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,F"I'm proud to call them my colleagues
OL,8,Fand am in awe of their resilience to
OL,9,Fcontinue ... turning up day and night
OL,10,Fknowing that whenever they get out of
OL,11,Fa vehicle more and more cameras are
OL,12,Ffocusing on their actions.
OL,14,F"But we shouldn't underestimate the
OL,15,Ftoll this has on them and their
OL,16,Ffamilies, and how off-putting it is to
OL,17,Fthe next generation who may think:
OL,18,F'Why would I put myself through that?'"
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@gO]
