OL,7,FSir Mark said it is now a regular
OL,8,Foccurrence for officers to find
OL,9,Fthemselves caught in the middle of
OL,10,Fpublic debate, "being accused of being
OL,11,Fboth woke and fascist for the exact
OL,12,Fsame actions".
OL,14,FHe bemoaned the level of abuse
OL,15,Fdirected at Metropolitan Police
OL,16,Fofficers, including one who posted a
OL,17,Fpicture of herself online at a
OL,18,Ffirearms event on International
OL,19,FWomen's Day.
OL,26,@rD@POUtD@MO]
