OL,7,FAnd the Commissioner said in the
OL,8,Fprevious 48 hours 12 officers had been
OL,9,Fhurt while on duty, including one who
OL,10,Fwas hit over the head with a bottle
OL,11,Fand another who was stabbed in the
OL,12,Fhand.
OL,14,FThe Met has suffered severe
OL,15,Freputational damage in recent years,
OL,16,Fincluding then-armed officer Wayne
OL,17,FCouzens committing rape and murder in
OL,18,FMarch 2021, and fellow marksman David
OL,19,FCarrick being unmasked as a serial
OL,20,Frapist.
